---
---

<section class="w-full px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto fade-in">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
      <span class="block w-5 h-[2px] bg-muted-2"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow text-ink-soft">A QUESTION</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-8">
      Does it feel like<br />
      time is <span class="highlight-purple">slipping away</span>
      <br />and you don't know where it went?
    </h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed">
      Most apps want your attention. Life Visor wants to give it back. It's a quiet companion that
      shows you, day by day, where your hours actually go — so you can decide what's worth keeping
      and what isn't.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-line bg-transparent">
      <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-info flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#255687" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
          <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink leading-snug">
        We all have the same 24 hours. <span class="font-bold">You decide how you spend them.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
